      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.73,
      "size": 27648,
      "text": "可是趋近到底是什么意思？多近才算近？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
