      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/xiaoxiao/challenge-chal-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "先由一个挑战者出场，他给出一个很小的正数 ε。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "challenge",
      "line_id": "chal-2",
