      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/xiaoxiao/challenge-chal-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.86,
      "size": 45792,
      "text": "ε 划出一条水平带，要求 f(x) 必须落在 L 上下不超过 ε 的范围内。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "challenge",
      "line_id": "chal-3",
      "filename": "challenge-chal-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/xiaoxiao/challenge-chal-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "ε 越小，这条水平带越窄，要求就越苛刻。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "response",
      "line_id": "resp-1",
