      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/xiaoxiao/response-resp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "我们的回应是找出一个 δ，划出一条竖直带，宽度是 a 左右各 δ。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "response",
      "line_id": "resp-2",
      "filename": "response-resp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/xiaoxiao/response-resp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.27,
      "size": 36288,
      "text": "只要 x 落在这条竖直带内，f(x) 就一定落在那条水平带内。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "response",
      "line_id": "resp-3",
      "filename": "response-resp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/epsilon-delta/xiaoxiao/response-resp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "图中绿色虚框，正是竖直带与水平带交出的安全区。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "epsilon-delta",
      "section_id": "forall",
